To make exe of a file 
1) Add 
    "bin":"./server.js",
    after name tag in package.json

2)Run command pkg .
3)Run the file



to install pkg 
    npm i pkg -g


document to pkg 
https://dev.to/jochemstoel/bundle-your-node-app-to-a-single-executable-for-windows-linux-and-osx-2c89.


to make only linux use 
    pkg . --target node10-linux-x64
